overview: On 1 January 2023, the New Year's Concert of the Vienna Philharmonic under the direction of Maestro Franz Welser-Möst took place at the Vienna Musikverein. Franz Welser-Möst has a particularly close and productive artistic partnership with the Vienna Philharmonic. He conducted the prestigious concert event for the third time after 2011 and 2013.  The 2023 New Year's Concert was broadcasted to over 90 countries worldwide and watched by millions of TV viewers.
tagline: New Year's Concert 2023 with Franz Welser-Möst
title: Neujahrskonzert der Wiener Philharmoniker 2023
